,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"可唔可以先滅咗共匪再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf638e8c9b0b4d45559bcdbf22a74c9712fc02a","tid":838963,"uid":61235,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"唔資助聯合國都要比人話,痴線到,遲D係街比人叫捐錢,唔肯捐分分鍾比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國退出左《巴黎協定》,不過排放量改善左好多,相反係呢個協定下個D國家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dccce0ad0b06a87e41a3dfa14229c460117da5","tid":838963,"uid":2974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣由選舉到而家剩係識講d好似好撚猛嘅野、擺下pose，攞得出手嘅政績一樣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400b4bc3fee0f4900e6bc5af2ebc96e2433dc49d","tid":838963,"uid":42636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"點解馬黑龍成日啄住侵侵？<br />\n唔係friend底咩"},{"pid":"ff1c505f2986cda2ff800772043161f24894a6d4","tid":838963,"uid":51828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"400b4bc3fee0f4900e6bc5af2ebc96e2433dc49d","tid":838963,"uid":42636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"點解馬黑龍成日啄住侵侵？<br />\n唔係friend底咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"左膠要講番左膠既Agenda,做埸戲姐唔洗咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c293fbd98a3206fd23ac0b886dcfa74a36c92bbe","tid":838963,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"法國隊.jpg"},{"pid":"6e305b165aa26cccd984576f478ae2ed5b3b7c37","tid":838963,"uid":20414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"搞掂自己先啦<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;法國星期三公布最新民調結果顯示, 總統馬克龍的支持率下滑至25%, 創下他就任法國總統以來新低.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;馬克龍的支持率與上月相比,下滑7個百分點. 民調同時顯示, 受訪者不支持馬克龍的比率達69%, 其中37%對馬克龍很不支持. 分析指馬克龍前保鏢打人的事發酵,法國經濟數據不佳等,打衝馬克龍的民望.<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;法國財政部本周公布的數據顯示, 法國2019年的財政赤字率將達2.8%,高於政府之前設定的2.3%的目標. 同時, 法國今年的經濟增速, 預計只有1.7%."},{"pid":"0edbeff1dfa36a5541bd4612beae66e4250991df","tid":838963,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20e13d4e6b5fb658026f4b2fe8f65d30765bcdb4","tid":838963,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"法國總統馬克龍任內做過d咩有成就既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:46:44.000Z","msg":"法國世盃奪冠"},{"pid":"b9acd0d7a69ee4c448edce9c68b59c3f62726f0d","tid":838963,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0edbeff1dfa36a5541bd4612beae66e4250991df","tid":838963,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20e13d4e6b5fb658026f4b2fe8f65d30765bcdb4","tid":838963,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"法國總統馬克龍任內做過d咩有成就既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T14:46:44.000Z","msg":"法國世盃奪冠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"係喎，完全醒唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff53455fd7d1139813530868bcaed8b8c58d52c4","tid":838963,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c09c1533f04140a1985bdcd7bdfcb62e06ec97d","tid":838963,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:42:04.000Z","msg":"同中共一齊團結起新疆集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}